manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Dynarex Baby Wipes - Non-Alcohol Wipes for Babies - Resealable Soft Pack - Non-Woven, Unscented - 5 x 7", 80 Wet Wipes per Pack, 24 per Case Need a Quick Solution for Sanitary Purposes? Despite the name, baby wipes are useful for more than just changing diapers. They’re a modern convenience that kids and adults of all ages can use to take care of spills, cool down dry skin, or help sanitize dirty or dusty surfaces. Even though dry toilet paper may be of some help with removing dry debris, pre-moistened wipes are sturdier and far better at picking up or cleaning off grime. They also come in conveniently portable packages, so you can always have a handful within easy reach. The Baby Wipes by Dynarex will help you conquer any mess.

For Baby Bottoms & Beyond A baby’s skin is delicate and prone to irritation. The longer their diapers go unchanged, the higher the risk of skin issues like rashes. Fortunately, a pack of our baby wipes can help you make quick work of diaper changes and other messy cleanups anytime you’re on the go. Baby wipes can also be used to wipe off excess lotion, sweat, and spilled food, as well as dirt, dust, mud, and anything else your little one can pick up from playing.

Non-Drying Formula Our wet wipes have a moisturizing formula with lanolin and aloe vera. It also does not contain alcohol, which can dry out and be harmful to the skin over time. Dry, weakened skin is then more susceptible to irritation and breakouts. We designed our baby wipes to be soothing and gentle enough to be used for daily cleansing. We also offer unscented baby wipes for those with sensitive skin.

Sturdy & Soft Although most wet wipes are made for single use, they can’t be effective if they’re flimsy or if they easily disintegrate. That’s why our baby wipes are made of a spun lace material that will hold up to rougher handling better than woven alternatives. These moist towelettes are soft, smooth, and cooling on the skin. They should also be just the right size to help you minimize waste and maximize wiping efficiency.

More Reasons to Love Our Baby Wipes: Portable Packs Our 5 x 7” and 7 x 8" scented or unscented baby wipes come in soft packs and tubs protected by sticker seals or hard plastic lids. These will help keep your supply moist and easier to travel with. They are suitable for home use and can be stored in your car or travel kits. Each pack or tub contains 80 wipes. If you require more supply, we also have canisters of Nice’n Fresh Premium Baby Wipes, carrying 140 pieces of 6x6.75” scented baby wipe Serves Every Purpose A pack of wet wipes can be useful in every situation. They are used in care facilities, schools, day cares, public restrooms, and cleaning stations. Not to mention, they should be present in every travel pack, medical care kit, or diaper bag. Our baby wipes can be helpful for general use — for sanitizing tools and equipment, or cleaning areas around irritation or wounds. You can order cases of 12 tubs or canisters, or cases of 24 soft packs. Because We Care Like Family At Dynarex, we're committed to providing outstanding service and premium-quality products. We offer a wide range of supplies, from disposables like wet wipes, gowns, and applicators, to important tools like walkers and ambulance equipment. We put our time and resources into ensuring that all our products meet industry standards, so we can help you give your customers the care they deserve.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Gives both my kids diaper rash
reviews.reviewText: Our daycare switched to these wipes and both my toddler and infant immediately got diaper rash. They switched back for a few months and the diaper rash disappeared. Daycare started using them again last week and both my kids came home with horrible rash.
